Nigerian movie director, Kemi Adetiba has traditionally tied the knot with her fiancé, Oscar Heman-Ackah in a quiet ceremony. The filmmaker disclosed this on Saturday via her official Instagram page, announcing her traditional marriage. She wrote, “This the day the Lord has made. We shall do a LOT of rejoicing, as we are so so glad in it Time to make it traditionally official. @oscarhemanackah #UndeniablyYours2022” Recall that Adetiba announced their engagement In February, 2022. POLL